name: 1000SATS (Ordinals)
description: SATS is a BRC-20 token that pays homage to satoshi. SATS is the abbreviation for satoshi, the smallest unit of Bitcoin. One satoshi equals to 0.00000001 BTC. Please note that the token is a meme token and is inscribed by an anonymous team.   1 KSATS = 1000 SATS
